(537, 'Trial and Terror', 'trial-and-terror', 'Unknown', 0, 4, 13, 305, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/trial-and-terror/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Stargazer Studio.', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Trial and Terror is the basic puzzle game In which you must control a small pixel square and navigate it out of the game area without colliding with any obstacles. Sometime the classics are simply the best and this game holds true to that value. Use your reaction and planning skills to successfully escape from the puzzle.\n', '', 'trial-and-terrorr.png', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 17:10:14', '2022-09-11 17:10:14', NULL),
