(1219, 'Undine Match the Pic', 'undine-match-the-pic', 'html5', 0, 5, 10, 674, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/aa3f22aaa18b465eaac404060fd13bb9/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/undine-match-the-pic', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'DL-studio', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In the summer you want to go to the sea, swim and sunbathe! And it\'s time to play another fun game. You need to find differences in two almost identical pictures. You will meet cute little mermaids and sea creatures, and train your mindfulness. Go ahead, hurry up before the time runs out. If you can’t find all the differences the first time, don’t be discouraged, try again, you will definitely succeed!', 'At each level, we look for differences between two similar pictures. The passage time is limited by a timer. Depending on the gaming device, a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touch screens is used to control.', 'undine-match-the-pic.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:06:44', '2022-09-11 22:06:44', NULL),
(1220, 'Be The Judge', 'be-the-judge', 'html5', 0, 5, 12, 459, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/10360ee341304524acd425210491f74a/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/be-the-judge', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Bermuda Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'It\'s hard job. Not everyone can do this. You are a judge. Something happened in your town and you need to decide who is right who is guilty.', 'Use mouse to select choice', 'be-the-judge.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:06:47', '2022-09-11 22:06:47', NULL),
(1221, 'Gurido', 'gurido', 'html5', 0, 5, 10, 561, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0685ec10b09848ec86fd3068a894db55/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/gurido', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Okashi Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gurido is a minimalistic puzzle game.\n\nAt the top of a 10x10 grid of cells, they have an irregularity shaped and coloured figure. By dragging these in a blank space of the grid, let create sets of five or more cells of same color to clear the connected cells.\nWith a big series of connected cells and some luck, catch powerful items to clear more cells.\n\nDo your best!', 'At the top of a 10x10 grid of cells, they have an irregularity shaped and coloured figure. By dragging these in a blank space of the grid, let create sets of five or more cells of same color to clear the connected cells.\nWith a big series of connected cells and some luck, catch powerful items to clear more cells.', 'gurido.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:06:49', '2022-09-11 22:06:49', NULL),
(1222, 'Zen Cube 3D', 'zen-cube-3d', 'html5', 0, 5, 15, 1007, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2a1b01b50c6b45a69350ec6ee1ff9ad3/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/zen-cube-3d', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Albayoo', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Zen Cube 3D is a relaxation match 3d puzzle game. Not like classic match games, Zen Triple 3D not only a time-killing game but also is a zen & relaxation matching puzzle game which is easy for everyone to play.', '- You need to choose 3 same 3D cubes.\n- Swipe to rotate the 3D cube, you can find more matching tile pairs.\n- Pay attention to the collecting bar, do not fill it up.\n- Use props at the right time to help you go more smoothly.\n- Focus on your senses, clear all tiles within limited time.', 'zen-cube-3d.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:06:52', '2022-09-11 22:06:52', NULL),
(1270, 'Birds Hex Jigsaw', 'birds-hex-jigsaw', 'html5', 0, 3, 13, 431, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b589e04b73934293a19942fc658c85ea/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/birds-hex-jigsaw', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Birds Hex Jigsaw is a different flavor of classical jigsaw game. Arrange the hex pieces of a picture to form the original picture. There are 2 modes in the games. Each mode has 24 levels. You must complete a level within time limits.', 'Use any pointing (mouse, touchpad etc) device to play this game.', 'birds-hex-jigsaw.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:08:25', '2022-09-11 22:08:25', NULL),
(1271, 'Wo-Miners', 'wo-miners', 'html5', 0, 4, 19, 642, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/60ed8a50f6be4403af405297ff124957/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/wo-miners', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Bermuda Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Are you a true harvester? Collect cottons on the ground and trade them with clothes. Try to find all shops and cottons you need to harvest on the map. And guardians will allow you to enter the castle.', 'Use mouse to use joystick to find hidden elements in map.', 'wo-miners.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:08:28', '2022-09-11 22:08:28', NULL),
(1272, 'Candy Rain 7', 'candy-rain-7', 'html5', 0, 5, 15, 25, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bb8da035bcac408090ccdf9aa01d6a7f/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/candy-rain-7', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'SOFTGAMES – Mobile Entertainment Services GmbH', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Candy Rain 7, one of greatest Match 3 games of all time! It’s the only Match 3 Game to have the lucky 7 sequels! Because of its huge popularity, the players simply asked for more. Candy Rain 7 boasts more levels, more candies, more waffles, more chests of coins and fun packed saga map to enjoy!', 'Find, match and catch candies, waffles and chests full of coins. Use powerful boosters and create rewarding combos to beat the high score in every single level! And the best thing about it? All of this fun is still absolutely calorie free and doesn\'t cost money either! Play and enjoy Candy Rain 7 now for free!', 'candy-rain-7.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:08:32', '2022-09-11 22:08:32', NULL),
(1273, 'Traffic Control Time', 'traffic-control-time', 'html5', 0, 3, 20, 764, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1265ebf8ad9346e59f3d87731f2d10ba/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/traffic-control-time', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a traffic control game where you control the flow of traffic by starting the traffic in a lane by clicking a clock which shows the correct time asked in the question. \n\nThere are four sets of clocks; each is connected to a traffic light signal. If you tap a clock showing the asked time, it will make its signal green and rest all will signals will be red. In each level you have to control the traffic for a limited time. Try to solve as many questions as you can, while avoiding the traffic congestion. If you tap the wrong clock, you will lose the level.  Game will be tougher gradually as you progress the levels. Try this to see how many points you can get in this game?', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'traffic-control-time.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:08:35', '2022-09-11 22:08:35', NULL),
