(1277, 'Clock Puzzle for Kids', 'clock-puzzle-for-kids', 'html5', 0, 5, 11, 1015, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e1d732b2c1eb486a844ea2904d1a6c30/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/clock-puzzle-for-kids', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Smart Play Studios', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Clock Puzzle is a fun game to learn how to tell time. This elementary activity is great fun for all children in the computer lab or at home! Kids will learn by trying to guess the time on the clocks.\n\nKids often develop misconceptions about concepts in mathematics, including time. It is important to help them get over those misconceptions. The game gives students an opportunity to learn more.', 'Tell the time to win more points.', 'clock-puzzle-for-kids.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:08:50', '2022-09-11 22:08:50', NULL),
