(1344, 'Fruit Blocks Puzzles', 'fruit-blocks-puzzles', 'html5', 0, 5, 20, 438, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/12f45ad1782f42689538a7527d3e0839/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/fruit-blocks-puzzles', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Fruit Blocks Puzzles is a block collapse game.Click on 2 or more than 2 similar fruit blocks to eliminate them. To complete a level you need to eliminate all the blocks on the board. Be wise while eliminating blocks because each block need at least one identical neighbor!', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'fruit-blocks-puzzles.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:11:41', '2022-09-11 22:11:41', NULL),
(1345, 'Reach 100 Colors Game', 'reach-100-colors-game', 'html5', 0, 4, 10, 125, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a3376d92315d4ba4835eed8d9c0f961b/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/reach-100-colors-game', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Playtouch', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Reach 100 is a game about puzzle and reflexion in which you must regroup numbers  to create sums of 100.  You have the possibility to slide the different forms and numbers, horizontally and vertically, and add numbers to each other.  If you reach the sum of 100, this form freezes and cannot be used anymore.  Regroup all forms to reach the end of the level.\nPut your neurons to the trial and find the solutions on sixty different levels. Levels are becoming more and more complexes.', 'you have to group the numbers to create sums of 100. You have the possibility to drag the different shapes and numbers, horizontally and vertically, and add numbers to each other', 'reach-100-colors-game.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:11:44', '2022-09-11 22:11:44', NULL),
(1346, 'Move The Pin 2', 'move-the-pin-2', 'html5', 0, 3, 18, 652, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/70105003e6cc40d4ab9c62e5d03a8649/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/move-the-pin-2', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Fun Best Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Move The Pin 2 is a game in which you need to fill a glass with colored balls, for this you also need to paint the gray balls with a colored bomb, you also need red prickly pins and bombs that can destroy the balls, and some foams are blocked.', 'Use mouse or touch the screen!', 'move-the-pin-2.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:11:47', '2022-09-11 22:11:47', NULL),
(1347, 'Hexagon', 'hexagon', 'html5', 0, 5, 19, 327, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/66007161a825414282a30db6a409fff0/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/hexagon-2', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'K17 Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hexagon is a strategy board game with puzzle elements that involves two players playing on a hexagonal grid. The rules are really simple, but the strategies are not. You will learn the game in a minute, but mastering Hexagon can take a lifetime.\nThe object of the game is to make your pieces constitute a majority of the pieces on the board at the end of the game, by converting as many of your opponent\'s pieces as possible.\nThe game will test your tactic skills and entertain you and your friends.', 'Tap and click on the pieces to move or duplicate them. Capture your opponent\'s pieces to gain advantage. The game has a built-in tutorial.', 'hexagon.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:11:50', '2022-09-11 22:11:50', NULL),
(1348, '3 PIECES GAME', '3-pieces-game', 'html5', 0, 5, 10, 22, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4f9b8433efa3486d91f8ca34aafafcbd/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/3-pieces-game', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'nau.games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, '3 PIECES GAME\n\nWith the game 3 PIECES GAME you learn which objects are related and put them together in a fun way from your mobile phone, tablet, or computer.\n\nGame developed by:\n\nNau.kids', 'Join related objects.', '3-pieces-game.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:11:53', '2022-09-11 22:11:53', NULL),
(1349, 'Squid Collection', 'squid-collection', 'html5', 0, 4, 16, 1112, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2534d8f4f00e47b2bca4d3be9ee06482/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/squid-collection', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'WillingGames.com', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Collect the squid items in this html5 game. Press any easter item to start. Now move the \'mouse or finger tip\' on identical adjacent items (horizontally, vertically or diagonally). Select at least 3 items. Release mouse button to make them match. Each 6th items will give a bonus. More than 7 items will give you a time bonus. Collect the target squid items within the giving time, or you will lose the game. What\'s the max level can you play?', 'Use mouse or tap to play this game.', 'squid-collection.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:11:56', '2022-09-11 22:11:56', NULL),
(1350, 'Fishing Puzzles', 'fishing-puzzles', 'html5', 0, 3, 16, 153, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9223a6e5ad604e9f8bba0842ee5612df/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/fishing-puzzles', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a board puzzle game where you need to remove all the fish on the board. Tap on the 2 similar fish which are in the same row or column.  It will catch all the fish between both fish including them. There are 24 challenges.', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'fishing-puzzles.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:11:59', '2022-09-11 22:11:59', NULL),
(1351, 'Get the Stars - Extended', 'get-the-stars-extended', 'html5', 0, 5, 16, 455, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ee2a54fb3bba454bb522fcddbb2338c8/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/get-the-stars-extended', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Misc.261 Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, '“Get the Stars - Extended” is a casual puzzle game. with 100 levels The goal is to collect all the stars of each area and get the keys to unlock your path to the next challenge.', 'Touch, PC (Mouse, Arrows, WASD, Gamepad (Player Move, Restart))', 'get-the-stars-extended.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:12:01', '2022-09-11 22:12:01', NULL),
(1352, 'Cute Puzzle', 'cute-puzzle', 'html5', 0, 3, 11, 701, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/141fb6d10a154e00b812fcad705d8a6a/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/cute-puzzle', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Vi Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Fantastic Puzzle game with a cute cartoon animals. Drag and drop the picture pieces to their exact locations. This game is free to play, no download needed. Complete all the 9 levels to win this game.', 'Mouse or tap to play.', 'cute-puzzle.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:12:04', '2022-09-11 22:12:04', NULL),
(1353, 'Word Search', 'word-search', 'html5', 0, 4, 19, 1064, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c13ee9c06edc4f0a8d7f6f291a7c13d8/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/word-search-2', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'SOFTGAMES – Mobile Entertainment Services GmbH', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Word Search is one of the best word games to exercise your brain, vocabulary as well as pattern recognition. The goal of Word Search is to find all the words that are listed next to the puzzle grid. The words are hidden inside the puzzle grid and go in all directions: horizontal, vertical, diagonal as well as backwards. Go to the calendar to find more puzzles. Come back every day for at least a few minutes to exercise your mind and the brain!', 'Find words by swiping through with your finger or by using your mouse to drag and highlight words within the puzzle grid. If you need help, use the hint function (under the bulb).', 'word-search.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:12:07', '2022-09-11 22:12:07', NULL),
(1354, 'Protect Emojis', 'protect-emojis', 'html5', 0, 4, 12, 1078, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/89f98ee9549c4761b363fe875be13527/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/protect-emojis', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'QkyGames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Look at these smiling emojis they are in danger of evil balls ready to attack them.\nDraw lines to protect the emojis, you will need all your wisdom and imagination.\nIt\'s time to help them! Can you protect them?', 'Touch and drag to draw a line.', 'protect-emojis.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:12:10', '2022-09-11 22:12:10', NULL),
(1355, 'Solitaire Klondike', 'solitaire-klondike', 'html5', 0, 4, 12, 685, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6eb544b6de27450c8a46e424819b89a7/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/solitaire-klondike-1', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Armath', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The addictive game you’ve been playing on your computer for years now goes wherever you do. Whether you know it as Patience, Klondike, or just Solitaire, this popular game is one of the best games around.', 'Tap or drag cards to arrange them in descending order with alternating colors. When you can, move cards up to the foundation to sort all of the suits from Ace to King. You can draw one card at a time for a more relaxing game, or draw three for a challenge to train your brain!', 'solitaire-klondike.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:12:12', '2022-09-11 22:12:12', NULL),
(1356, 'Hidden Animals', 'hidden-animals', 'html5', 0, 3, 10, 654, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e10676fbd9f346809c3d334af21c572b/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/hidden-animals', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hidden Animals is an skill based puzzle game where you need to find all the hidden animals in the forest. You need to complete all 8 challenging levels to win this game.', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'hidden-animals.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:12:15', '2022-09-11 22:12:15', NULL),
(1404, 'Word Swipe', 'word-swipe', 'html5', 0, 4, 11, 1124, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ef4b392680554564abe1a3d3917a754b/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/word-swipe', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'SOFTGAMES – Mobile Entertainment Services GmbH', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Word Swipe is one of the most popular and fun word games ever made. It guarantees hours of intellectual fun that will exercise your both your mind and vocabulary. Come back every day for at least a few minutes to exercise your brain!', 'Find and create words by swiping through at least 3 letters! The longer the word, the more points you get. Be careful, there is a time limit for every level! How many levels can you go through? Will you become a master?', 'word-swipe.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:13:58', '2022-09-11 22:13:58', NULL),
(1405, 'Cute Puppies Puzzle', 'cute-puppies-puzzle', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 599, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9c035565bd214593b6f1ba6fc59bb165/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/cute-puppies-puzzle-1', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'DL-studio', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'It\'s time for puzzles! Just look at these cute and funny puppies. They love to eat delicious food, fly into space and love ice cream. Test your wits. Collect all the pictures with these wonderful puppies and have fun!', 'Collection of puzzles with episodes from the life of cute little dogs. The game must be completed as quickly as possible, and your result can be saved as a picture-certificate. Depending on the gaming device, a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touch screen is used for control.', 'cute-puppies-puzzle.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:02', '2022-09-11 22:14:02', NULL),
(1406, 'Solitaire Chess', 'solitaire-chess', 'html5', 0, 4, 16, 636, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/68c8077190be41c0bc61aff5d04ecf99/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/solitaire-chess', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'K17 Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Solitaire Chess is an addictive puzzle game vaguely based on chess, but you don\'t have to be a grandmaster to play it. The rules are simple - move your pieces the same way as in chess, performing an obligatory capture every turn. The objective is to capture all pieces on the board leaving just a sole one standing.\nKnowing chess rules is not required - the game has a built-in tutorial and a cheat-sheet for moves.\n', 'Take and move any piece with a mouse (or finger on mobile)\nAll the pieces follow their respective chess moving patterns\nCapture all the pieces on the board leaving only one (any will do)\nGet a tip if you get stuck\n', 'solitaire-chess.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:06', '2022-09-11 22:14:06', NULL),
(1407, 'Food Tiles Match 3', 'food-tiles-match-3', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 881, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b14f2c5f5a4d42dc9c261eeb3594e50a/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/food-tiles-match-3', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'BestGamesFreePlay.com', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a fun and exciting match-3 game. You need to match 3 or more tiles in the same row or column to collect them. Collect all the required tiles in each level to complete it.', 'Tap and swipe to switch the tiles.\nYou need to match 3 or more tiles in the same row or column to collect them.', 'food-tiles-match-3.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:09', '2022-09-11 22:14:09', NULL),
(1408, 'Impulse Ball', 'impulse-ball', 'html5', 0, 4, 11, 440, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0ca64f7a71584bdab61072b40d3b36e9/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/impulse-ball', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Fun Best Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Virtual golf can look like anything and a set: a player, a club, a ball and a hole is not necessary at all. The game Impulse Ball will have a ball, a hole and fields in the form of labyrinths on forty-five levels. Instead of a club, you will use momentum. Click behind the ball to push it there. Where do you want him to get to, namely the hole with the red flag. Labyrinths become more difficult, longer, you will have to try hard to score the ball. As soon as he is in the hole, a fountain of fireworks will appear. Please note that the number of impulses is limited, so do not make unnecessary movements in the Impulse Ball.', 'Use mouse or touch the screen!', 'impulse-ball.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:13', '2022-09-11 22:14:13', NULL),
(1409, 'Black Stallion Cabaret', 'black-stallion-cabaret', 'html5', 0, 4, 10, 260, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/729f6224fce341cdb068b821c1006cc7/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/black-stallion-cabaret', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'PERSONA•GAMES', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'What else do you need if you have an armored train? That\'s right, a whole train carriage full of charming dancers! Get them through the whole country entertaining the public in towns, improving your train and repel the attacks of monsters.\nThe goal of the game is to get the dancers through the whole country and protect them from monsters.\nIn the main mode of the game you need to merge items you create in the workshop to increase their level and improve weapons, dancers and the workshop.\nYou need weapons to defend against the large amount of monsters you\'ll meet on your way. The battles are automatic. You have 30 seconds to eliminate a squad of monsters. Dancers give performances in towns and get rewards including details for the train cars. With details you can buy new train cars and improve the current ones.', '- Merge items and increase their level. The higher the level of an item, the more points it gives while using it.\n- Items are used for improving weapons, dancers and the workshop. Double click on an item to use it.\n- Defeat the monster squads to move to the next town.\n- Get carriage parts in the town and level up your train. The number of parts depends on the level of dancers.\n- The level of the workshop influence the maximum level of crafted items and the size of the warehouse.', 'black-stallion-cabaret.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:16', '2022-09-11 22:14:16', NULL),
(1410, 'Bubble Shooter - Farm Fruit', 'bubble-shooter-farm-fruit', 'html5', 0, 5, 10, 1053, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f6031432cc124865886970db7721b1ff/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/bubble-shooter-farm-fruit', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'goolgames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Big Teddy needs your help! Pop the bubbles to rescue the mini teddy bears. Place your bubble shooter aim carefully to clear the maximum amount of bubbles in each level. Features: - Interactive tutorial - 20 challenging levels - Fun theme - Solve bubble sets using a variety of tactics. Use clever theory of angles, target higher bubbles and other tactics to solve each level', 'Pop the bubbles to rescue the mini teddy bears.', 'bubble-shooter-farm-fruit.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:20', '2022-09-11 22:14:20', NULL),
(1411, 'Potato Chips Simulator', 'potato-chips-simulator', 'html5', 0, 4, 17, 496, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/351a0f39081c420fbf1f6c71fb2195f0/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/potato-chips-simulator', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'TrendyGames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Here\'s a great simulation for potato chip lovers. A whole process awaits you, from planting potatoes to selling them as chips in the market. Go step by step and place the delicious chips on the shelves! So let\'s start.', 'Game played with MOUSE.', 'potato-chips-simulator.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:23', '2022-09-11 22:14:23', NULL),
(1412, '1 Block Puzzles', '1-block-puzzles', 'html5', 0, 4, 15, 544, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/64df6c1b396e4ef5b4ad2f8fa0d21e34/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/1-block-puzzles', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'It is a challenging puzzle game. Playing this game is very simple. You need to make blocks to jump over other blocks. It will eliminate a block from the board. To complete a level, eliminate all the blocks except one, which jumps last. Complete all 24 levels to win this game.', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', '1-block-puzzles.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:27', '2022-09-11 22:14:27', NULL),
(1413, 'Mahjong Alchemy', 'mahjong-alchemy', 'html5', 0, 5, 10, 384, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/05ff9c8b10a447739074c8c676a3193b/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/mahjong-alchemy', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Little Missle', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Collect the same cards by simply selecting them on the screen! Train your memory and improve your attentiveness to find pairs even faster! Remember, the faster you open a pair, the more points you will get! At the same time, enjoy the atmosphere of a Chinese festival and the magic of alchemy on the road or after a hard day\'s work! The game is perfect for relaxing and getting only positive emotions! Also, do not forget to buy new cards! The more beautiful and rare the card, the more expensive it is, but believe me, it\'s worth it!', 'Connect identical cards by simply clicking on them. The faster you do it, the more points you will get! Can\'t find a couple? Use the hint by clicking on the corresponding button on the side. If this did not help, then try to move for coins. Also, you can buy new cards for coins. The cooler the card, the more expensive it is', 'mahjong-alchemy.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:31', '2022-09-11 22:14:31', NULL),
(1414, 'Help Me: Time Travel Adventure', 'help-me-time-travel-adventure', 'html5', 0, 5, 11, 241, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8f9320abd4d74e2d89a82f782c61db9b/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/help-me:-time-travel-adventure', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Brosco Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Everyone has been eagerly waiting for it, and now it\'s finally here! A fascinating puzzle game where you need to find the right answer. If you pick the wrong choice, the hero won\'t be rescued. A game focused on both difficult logic and relaxation, so you\'ll have to put your brain into action and use your IQ to solve the puzzles.', 'How to play:\nYou have a choice from several options, of which only one is correct! not everyone can solve these complex tests; you will need to use your wit and brain. The wrong options can lead to funny results for the hero.\nYou can choose your appearance out of dozens of clothing items, a set that gives you hundreds of variations. You can choose options that allow you to look like whoever you want, from a botanist to a rock star.', 'help-me-time-travel-adventure.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:34', '2022-09-11 22:14:34', NULL),
(1415, 'Tangram Grid', 'tangram-grid', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 331, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/57ee85b9766247cfaf57d1591b9c8e36/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/tangram-grid', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Misc.261 Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tangram Grid is a puzzle game to fill all the grids using seven pieces. Make sure to place all of them correctly with no overlap to complete each level.', 'Use the left mouse button to drag and drop the pieces, and click the pieces to rotate.', 'tangram-grid.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:38', '2022-09-11 22:14:38', NULL);
