(1416, 'Cube Blast', 'cube-blast', 'html5', 0, 5, 14, 490, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/39f56d81044d4ce9b713bf092048a331/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/cube-blast-1', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'SNSHUB', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, '\nMatch two or more blocks of the same color to clear the level! Your puzzle skills will be tested with hours of block busting fun!Take on this puzzling alone or play with friends to see who can get the highest score!\n\n', 'Match two or more blocks of the same color to clear the level', 'cube-blast.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:41', '2022-09-11 22:14:41', NULL),
(1417, 'Tasty Match', 'tasty-match', 'html5', 0, 4, 20, 342, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/224cba30a91a42debb44da41b7ff1866/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/tasty-match', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Z Media', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A colorful and addictive game to relax and unwind!\n\nThe goal of the game is to connect pairs of identical tiles.\nYou need to have time to clear the entire field before the time runs out.\n\nConnect more distant tiles to get more stars.\n\nFor a certain number of stars, a reward is given - a chest.\n\nOver time, new beautiful tiles are unlocked and level configurations become more complicated.', 'The goal of the game is to connect pairs of identical tiles.\n\nYou need to have time to clear the entire field of how the time runs out.\n\nConnect more distant tiles to get more stars.\n\nFor a certain number of stars, a reward is given - a chest.', 'tasty-match.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:45', '2022-09-11 22:14:45', NULL),
(1418, 'Jigsaw Hero', 'jigsaw-hero', 'html5', 0, 5, 12, 58, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f4bf890f28ba4a4aba4a5915bc63a308/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/jigsaw-hero', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Mabno', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Enjoy this challenging and funny puzzle game! Just rotate the pieces and complete the picture. Wait, it\'s not as easy as it sounds, 15 pictures to test your skills! Animals, cars and castles are the photos waiting you to resolve.\nUpload your own pictures and play with them!\nWhen you finish each picture, you can download a certificate!', 'Tap to rotate the piece', 'jigsaw-hero.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:49', '2022-09-11 22:14:49', NULL),
(1419, 'Drop n Merge Blocks', 'drop-n-merge-blocks', 'html5', 0, 3, 17, 733, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/03f5f469cdaa4746acc42ad3f4504bae/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/drop-n-merge-blocks', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Playtouch', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'DROP AND MERGE THE NUMBERS is a new kind of game like 2048. Just drop a block, it will automatically merge with identical numbers that are near it. It can create a chain reaction if you are good enough. How many blocks can you unify and what score can you reach before you loose?', 'You have to drop a block, and it automatically merges with the identical numbers that are nearby', 'drop-n-merge-blocks.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:53', '2022-09-11 22:14:53', NULL),
(1420, 'Candy Match 2', 'candy-match-2', 'html5', 0, 4, 18, 340, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b7fa8114cc314034bded77944a9c37c8/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/candy-match-2-1', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'SOFTGAMES – Mobile Entertainment Services GmbH', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This beautiful Match 3 Game takes you on a journey through the beautiful land of candies. Combine and collect cute candies in over 2000+ Exciting Levels! Complete the Daily Missions and Daily Challenges to earn additional coins and other gifts!', 'The more candies and other items of the same kind you combine with one match, the stronger the power-ups are you get in return! Go on an adventure through the beautiful land of Candies. Help your host remove stones and other obstacles, to collect candies or go treasure hunting. Beware anyone who tries to stop you on your journey! Enjoy this beautiful Match 3 Game with 2000+ challenging levels!', 'candy-match-2.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:14:59', '2022-09-11 22:14:59', NULL),
(1421, 'Toy Car Jigsaw', 'toy-car-jigsaw', 'html5', 0, 4, 19, 650, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/43ab086b07624b86a8dc73b9dc57d559/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/toy-car-jigsaw', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Fun Best Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Toy Car Jigsaw is a fun online puzzle game. Drag the pieces into right position using mouse. Solving puzzles is relaxing, rewarding, and keeps your brain sharp. You need to spend $1000 to be able to purchase one of the following pictures. You have three modes for each picture from which the hardest mode brings more money. You have a total of 10 pictures.', 'Use mouse or touch the screen!', 'toy-car-jigsaw.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:15:02', '2022-09-11 22:15:02', NULL),
(1422, 'Block Magic Puzzle', 'block-magic-puzzle', 'html5', 0, 5, 13, 1142, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8c8bb24aa9394da494a6b6d7e2141b3b/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/block-magic-puzzle', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Illusions Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Block Magic Puzzle is similar to the classic Tetris game, but differs in the mechanics of building blocks, which makes it exciting and diverse.\nIn addition, you will have access to competitions with other players, achievements and a lot of unforgettable emotions when you beat your own record!', 'It is necessary to move the blocks from the bottom panel with three random blocks to the playing field.\n\nThe main goal is to score as many points as possible. Points are awarded when placing a block on the map and for destroying lines with blocks.\nThe loss occurs when there is no free space left on the card to install the block.', 'block-magic-puzzle.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:15:05', '2022-09-11 22:15:05', NULL),
(1423, 'Among Float Connect', 'among-float-connect', 'html5', 0, 4, 14, 818, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d433706c75ba4e15be369d5df9822bed/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/among-float-connect', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'GamesFine.com', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Connect 2 same among items with a path that no more than two 90 degree angles. Clear the board by removing all pairs of identical among items. Becareful, in some levels the item tiles can float ( to bottom, to uper, to left, to right, to center or split). There are 27 challenging levels in this game. Complete a level before time bounds to get extra bonus.', 'Use mouse to click the same tiles to clear them.', 'among-float-connect.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:15:08', '2022-09-11 22:15:08', NULL),
(1471, 'Secrets of the Castle - Match 3', 'secrets-of-the-castle-match-3', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 1044, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0d0c9814cb8249f0b25def77df54515f/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/secrets-of-the-castle-match-3', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'AnimaGames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Solve all the secrets of the mysterious castle!\nSecrets of the Castle - play this challenging match 3 game for free! Collect three crystals in a line and complete the levels!\nIn the game you will find many difficult levels, obstacles and worthy rewards, as well as endless lives!\nThis match 3 game already has more than five thousand levels!\nGame Features:\nOver 5000 exciting logic levels!\nVarious obstacles and bonuses!\nMystical graphics and soundtrack!\nPlay this match 3 game for free!', 'The rules of the game are that you must move the crystals so as to combine three crystals in a row! But not everything is so simple - in this you will be hindered by obstacles that not everyone can overcome!\nBy combining crystals 3 in a row, you break obstacles and complete tasks on levels. Some of them are very difficult and you will have to try hard to pass them!', 'secrets-of-the-castle-match-3.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:17:00', '2022-09-11 22:17:00', NULL),
(1472, 'Voxel Merge 3D', 'voxel-merge-3d', 'html5', 0, 5, 14, 496, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c3eb535d0139450d9b2c38589a8430f6/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/voxel-merge-3d', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Brosco Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'If you have a spare minute, you should play our game Voxel Merge 3D. In the game you have to find pairs of objects and match them to sort out the pile of objects on the screen. The style of the game is reminiscent of the famous game Mine Craft, which will allow you to re-immerse yourself in the atmosphere of pixel style.\nAfter completing each level, you can unlock new items, get rubies to compete with other players on the rankings.\nIn order for the game not to seem boring to you, we have added pickaxes, like in Mine Craft. As your level increases, you can buy stronger pickaxes to break new types of blocks. The higher level the block you smash, the cooler merge items you\'ll get on the table.\nWith its voxel-style three-dimensional graphics, pickaxe pumping system, and unique match-finding game mechanics, Voxel Merge 3D stands out from all other games.\nYou\'ll love our game. Enjoy and good luck.', 'Merge items\nBreak blocks\nUpgrade Pickaxes\nBuy different bonus', 'voxel-merge-3d.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:17:04', '2022-09-11 22:17:04', NULL),
(1473, 'Air Slip', 'air-slip', 'html5', 0, 3, 13, 137, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6d363e7f6eba46fa8c89ea3cb5cd01b2/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/air-slip', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'newgamess', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Air Slip is a game where you need to control the beam. There is a green ball on the beam that moves along the beam as it rotates. From the top of the game come cubes in green and purple color. The object of the game is to catch the green cubes with the green ball on the beam and avoid the purple ones. The result counts only if you catch a green cube. With every purple cube you touch, you lose a life. You have the right to three errors, after that game ends.', 'Tap on screen to change rotate direction of the beam.', 'air-slip.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:17:07', '2022-09-11 22:17:07', NULL),
(1474, 'CrateMage', 'cratemage', 'html5', 0, 5, 11, 1004, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4872d69c1b5b405784f4b6e194213508/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/cratemage', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Digital Oddities', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A puzzle filled dungeon where your command of crates if your only hope to locate the treasure deep within! Use your magical orbs to link together crates and have their movement synchronized to overcome a series of mind melting challenges.', 'WASD to move.\nLeft mouse button over a crate to link an orb.\nRight mouse button over a crate to unlink an orb.\nSpacebar recalls all orbs.\nM mutes the music.\nR restarts the level.', 'cratemage.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:17:11', '2022-09-11 22:17:11', NULL),
