(1476, 'Aquatic Blocks', 'aquatic-blocks', 'html5', 0, 3, 16, 1090, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bc4a1a8d4975442a909702ea19771437/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/aquatic-blocks', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Aquatic Blocks is a classic block collapse game where you need to eliminate all the blocks in a level. You can remove a group of similar blocks which are adjacent linearly. If you try to remove a single block 200 points will be deducted from your score. Number of block types and level target will be increased gradually. Check how far you can go in this game?', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'aquatic-blocks.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:17:18', '2022-09-11 22:17:18', NULL),
