(1873, 'Bubble Hunt', 'bubble-hunt', 'html5', 0, 4, 14, 577, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a709267815c84616a1945c1958d9f5a1/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/bubble-hunt', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Bubble Hunt is a Classical bubble shooter game with 48 challenges. Aim and release the bubble in order to combine it with other similar bubbles. Your goal is to collect the Golden heart within the allowed time. Don’t let the bubbles reach the border. There are several power-ups which can be activated by shooting bubble on them.', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'bubble-hunt.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:17', '2022-09-11 22:31:17', NULL),
(1874, 'Boxman Sokoban', 'boxman-sokoban', 'html5', 0, 5, 13, 778, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ef7f51b95fa84d5a9832b4df4c974a3c/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/boxman-sokoban', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'WillingGames.com', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Boxman Sokoban is a free classic box-pushing puzzle game. The objective is to put all the boxes in the marked positions by pushing one at a time. There are 100 levels to play.', 'Desktop: Use arrow keys or WASD to move the boxman, Z to undo, and R to restart.\nMobile: Swipe to move.\n\nOr you can use the Buttons UI to control and play.', 'boxman-sokoban.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:20', '2022-09-11 22:31:20', NULL),
(1875, 'Solitaire Master-Classic Card', 'solitaire-master-classic-card', 'html5', 0, 5, 11, 675, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/799f93b0ae7543a7a8406fe7d3a539e2/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/solitaire-master-classic-card', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'XTStudio', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Solitaire by XT Studios is the new best way to play the classic card game you know and love for FREE, offline and online!\n\nThe most popular card game in the world, classic Solitaire Master-Classic Card, also known as Patience, is a great way to relax and train your brain. With beautiful graphics, fun animations, and free, offline play, Solitaire is the best game to pass the time.', 'Solitaire Master uses a standard 52 card deck of playing cards without jokers. The objective of the game is to expose all cards and move them into the foundation piles. There are 4 foundation piles (one for each suit) that are represented on the screen by an “A“ written on it. These piles are built upward in suit from Aces to Kings.', 'solitaire-master-classic-card.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:24', '2022-09-11 22:31:24', NULL),
(1876, 'Puzzling', 'puzzling', 'html5', 0, 5, 14, 653, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/49bad7a5f4b944ef995be0dc60af9795/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/puzzling', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'XTStudio', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Puzzline is an easy yet exciting way to exercise your brain and relax your mind on the go!\nExperience the benefits of line puzzles: on your way to work, before bed or whenever you need to kill time, this brand new brain training puzzle game is the perfect way to activate your brain while having fun! Simply drag the pegs and arrange the strings into amazing colorful designs like cats, rockets, flowers, and many more.', '• Drag the pegs into a hole.\n• Undo tangled and overlapping string!\n• Try to copy the suggested shape above.\n• Enjoy cute and cool designs by moving dots.', 'puzzling.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:27', '2022-09-11 22:31:27', NULL),
(1877, 'Happy Stars Match 3', 'happy-stars-match-3', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 168, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bc8c4f66741f4dfeb4ef3b50515c42a1/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/happy-stars-match-3', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Swap Stars in order to make a group of 3 or more identical stars adjacent horizontally or vertically.  Keep matching till you unlock and clear all the tiles. Use power-ups to speed up the process. Complete all the 36 levels to win this game.', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'happy-stars-match-3.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:30', '2022-09-11 22:31:30', NULL),
(1878, 'Destroy Figures', 'destroy-figures', 'html5', 0, 4, 16, 496, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b22d43a6769548208ffeb860d9677b06/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/destroy-figures', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Fun Best Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The brown ball in Destroy Figures is your weapon from which a mass of small balls will fly out. With them you will bombard white geometric shapes that will fall on top of you. At the same time, they will not fall one or two at a time, but will tumble down in a whole heap. You must quickly orient yourself and start a heavy bombardment around the entire perimeter, so as not to give a single figure break through the dotted border line. You have ten charges left, with which you must destroy a maximum of objects. Shoot the cluster, so you have a chance to hit several at once with one ball and save on the projectile.', 'Use mouse or touch the screen!', 'destroy-figures.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:32', '2022-09-11 22:31:32', NULL),
(1879, 'Resize Mahjong', 'resize-mahjong', 'html5', 0, 4, 15, 979, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bcb7f9669d364cddbad18b62cfc3c40f/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/resize-mahjong', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'bestphysics', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You need to find and match tiles with the same pictures of animals. Unlike regular mahjong, the game has tiles of different shapes and sizes. It is possible to combine tiles of the different sizes among themselves, the main thing that on them identical animals were represented.', 'Find tiles with the same animals to clear the entire playing field and free all 40 animals from captivity. You can use the hints and shuffle the tiles on the playing field.', 'resize-mahjong.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:35', '2022-09-11 22:31:35', NULL),
(1880, 'Gummy Blocks Battle', 'gummy-blocks-battle', 'html5', 0, 3, 14, 474, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0b49ff1616b24ec4a7683bcdade13b15/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/gummy-blocks-battle', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Code This Lab srl', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'If you are a fan of Gummy Blocks you\'ll surely love its Multiplayer version! \nChallenge real players all over the world! \nClear two or more lines to launch locks that will block your opponent! \nClear lines to get extra time.\nAre you ready?\nMay the best win!\n', 'Create or destroy full lines on the screen, both vertical and horizontal.\nClear two or more lines to launch locks to your opponent.\nClear lines to get extra time.', 'gummy-blocks-battle.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:38', '2022-09-11 22:31:38', NULL),
(1881, 'Jigsaw Puzzle Cats & Kitten', 'jigsaw-puzzle-cats-kitten', 'html5', 0, 5, 20, 1028, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ae1cca1f1c624827b417b98237a0829d/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/jigsaw-puzzle-cats-and-kitten', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Playtouch', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, '\"Jigsaw Puzzle Cats & Kitten \" is a classic jigsaw puzzle game but specifically designed for digital screens. You can drag and drop pieces like in a real jigsaw puzzle board game.\nThis jigsaw puzzle game is dedicated to cats and kitten. \nYou have the choise to play from easy puzzles from a couple of piece to very hard puzzles with hundred of pieces.You can also play with the daily challenge to unlock special items.', 'put the pieces of the puzzle together', 'jigsaw-puzzle-cats-kitten.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:41', '2022-09-11 22:31:41', NULL),
(1882, 'Cut Grass', 'cut-grass', 'html5', 0, 3, 10, 1091, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a9828f87cbe24c39a43484e52e0d749a/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/cut-grass', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Zapjee', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Cut Grass is a relaxing and beautiful lawn mower simulation and puzzle game. Become a Gardner and trim the grass and other shrubs. Cut the lawn for hours and grow beautiful flowers. Solve a variety of challenging and puzzling levels.', 'Swipe to cut the grass/ Use arrow keys.', 'cut-grass.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:44', '2022-09-11 22:31:44', NULL),
(1883, 'Fruits Coloring', 'fruits-coloring', 'html5', 0, 5, 18, 528, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cff985735f4845f4b0540044508eea1c/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/fruits-coloring', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A full featured coloring game with 18 nice sketches of fruits and vegetables. You can zoom in or zoom out the image to color more properly. You can also choose thickness of your pencil to fast and smart coloring.  After coloring you can save or print your colored image to share with your friends.', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'fruits-coloring.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:46', '2022-09-11 22:31:46', NULL),
(1884, 'Fill In the holes', 'fill-in-the-holes', 'html5', 0, 3, 19, 784, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d5a35aac5eb14a3fb5e2cb9ed4986bd2/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/fill-in-the-holes', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Playtouch', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Are you ready to play this fantastic puzzle game ? It is an easy game do not panic. \nFirst, look at the numbers on the grid. Each of them should fill the same amount of boxes/fiels. So if you see a 4, there should be 4 boxes near this tile that should be fill with this same color.\nI told you it\'s easy to understand... However, it\'s a bit harder to master on higher levels, but first ones are super easy to learn and to enjoy this nice puzzle game.', 'Each of them should fill the same amount of boxes/fiels', 'fill-in-the-holes.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:49', '2022-09-11 22:31:49', NULL),
(1885, 'Fairyland Pic Puzzles', 'fairyland-pic-puzzles', 'html5', 0, 3, 20, 852, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5f6c3824e9574fa0ab529bcdd37249ca/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/fairyland-pic-puzzles', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Fairyland pic puzzles is a simple puzzle game. You need to arrange the pieces of picture by rotating them to form the complete picture as shown in the right panel.', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'fairyland-pic-puzzles.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:52', '2022-09-11 22:31:52', NULL),
(1886, ' Stickman Warriors', 'stickman-warriors', 'html5', 0, 4, 15, 493, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/45404e8b6c0943428defb5be568d6793/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/stickman-warriors-1', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'XTStudio', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'An exiting game about a stickman escape from prison.\nA stickman is framed and imprisoned, but he never gives up and plans to self-salvation. Persevere, day after day, year after year. Hope can set him free. Finally, he can take the breath of freedom.', 'Cut the block, drop it to the floor, and you can step on the block to get out of the woods.', 'stickman-warriors.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:55', '2022-09-11 22:31:55', NULL),
(1887, 'Pipe Balls', 'pipe-balls', 'html5', 0, 3, 16, 250, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2a972d89f83443329983708011a39d0d/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/pipe-balls', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Bermuda Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In this exciting brain game, you have to bring all your intelligence and skill. You need to lead the balls from the machine to the goal cup. Sounds simple, right? It’s not! Because the pipes are disconnected, and it’s up to you to reconnect them in the right way.', 'Use mouse left button to click pipes and rotate them.', 'pipe-balls.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:31:58', '2022-09-11 22:31:58', NULL),
(1888, 'Happy Farm The Crop', 'happy-farm-the-crop', 'html5', 0, 4, 19, 940, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/616c481c1aea4b77b04637c3832955a7/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/happy-farm-the-crop', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Playtouch', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In this beautiful game, you have to collect the fruits and vegetables from your vegetable garden. It\'s easy to pick them, just find 2 pairs of identical tiles and click on them. It\'s like a game of mahjong but it\'s even more fun with the world of the countryside and the farm.\nNo fuss, just a good time with gorgeous graphics, lovable characters, and a game that\'s just plain fun to play.\nThere are plenty of different levels and environments that will allow you to play without ever getting bored.', 'Collect the fruits and vegetables in pairs.', 'happy-farm-the-crop.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:32:01', '2022-09-11 22:32:01', NULL),
(1889, 'Coloring Book Easter', 'coloring-book-easter', 'html5', 0, 5, 12, 940, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f0bc8c92c19343e9abb66ea0a84275e0/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/coloring-book-easter', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Fun Best Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a Coloring Book Easter, where he exercise her imagination and motor skills while having fun meeting different images. In this game you will find 18 different pictures which have to be colored. You have 15 different colors to choose. You can also save the colored image. Have fun!', 'Use mouse on desktop or touch on your mobile device.', 'coloring-book-easter.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:32:04', '2022-09-11 22:32:04', NULL),
(1890, 'Happy Easter Game', 'happy-easter-game', 'html5', 0, 5, 13, 509, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b70e01056411406bb1d72aa476981e59/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/happy-easter-game', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'newgamess', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In this game, you need to throw Easter eggs in the balloon basket. Try to put more eggs as you can in the basket. Take a position, aim, and shoot to the basket. But the rabbit that is in the balloon basket is a bad pilot and the balloon will not be stable at all. He will go up and down and left and right. For that reason will be harder to throw the eggs inside the basket. If you make a mistake and drop the eggs on the floor the new life will be born. The little chicks will hatch from the eggs.', 'Tap and slide on the screen to play this game.', 'happy-easter-game.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:32:06', '2022-09-11 22:32:06', NULL),
(1891, 'Diamond Colors Art', 'diamond-colors-art', 'html5', 0, 3, 18, 690, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b77bfce97c654976a7829afd2eba7f4f/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/diamond-colors-art', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'TrendyGames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Are you new to painting? Don\'t worry! Just fill the diamond into the canvas according to the number to complete a masterpiece of your own. There are a variety of pictures in the game for you to choose from! 101 different pictures are waiting for you in the gallery. In each level, the pictures are detailed and the number of colored diamonds increases.', 'Move: \"W,A,S,D or ARROW KEYS or MOUSE\"   \nZoom In / Out: \"MOUSE SCROLL\"', 'diamond-colors-art.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:32:09', '2022-09-11 22:32:09', NULL),
(1892, 'Recycling Time 2', 'recycling-time-2', 'html5', 0, 3, 20, 588, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/57dc1702f3e84cbfa81be77362065eea/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/recycling-time-2', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Rich Games ', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, '“Recycling Time 2” is the second game in the recycling franchise, where the player must clean nature by collecting trash and putting it in their respective trash cans, for recycling to be done correctly, thus helping the planet.', 'On Computer: Use mouse to play.\n\nOn Mobile: Use touch to play', 'recycling-time-2.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:32:12', '2022-09-11 22:32:12', NULL),
(1940, 'Find Unique Chick', 'find-unique-chick', 'html5', 0, 4, 20, 120, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5ded07428fa947fc87e5d6e63b50fd76/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/find-unique-chick', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a board puzzle game where you have to tap the unique Chick. All other Trees have their pair in board but one is unique. So try to find out unique chick before time runs out.', 'Tap the unique chick.', 'find-unique-chick.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:33:36', '2022-09-11 22:33:36', NULL),
