(2540, 'Tractor Coloring Pages', 'tractor-coloring-pages', 'html5', 0, 4, 12, 894, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5c1517abe66a489e98fc261f8ba16441/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/tractor-coloring-pages', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'newgamess', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tractor Coloring Pages is a kids coloring game with tractors. You can select one of twelve images with tractors in it and color it. On the right side of the game screen, you can find different colors. Click on it to use them. On the left side of the game screen, you can change the brush size. If you color a smaller area you will need to small the brush size. When you do some mistakes you can use an eraser to erase the error. So, Click play select the image, and start to color. You can save the image when you are done with coloring. Use the image later as you wish.', 'Use mouse to color or slide on the screen.', 'tractor-coloring-pages.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:55:39', '2022-09-11 22:55:39', NULL),
(2541, 'Battle Royale Puzzles', 'battle-royale-puzzles', 'html5', 0, 3, 18, 426, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6e40272c0d394ab8b6e4104fd4692d51/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/battle-royale-puzzles', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'New Kids Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Welcome to the game called Battle Royale Puzzles! In this game you have 12 puzzles with pictures from Fortnite. Assemble them by changing to place the pieces. To change drag parts up to another position. Completed a level, go to the next. In each level you have limited time for which need to complete it.', 'Use mouse or touch the screen!', 'battle-royale-puzzles.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:55:42', '2022-09-11 22:55:42', NULL),
(2542, 'Pop It Nums', 'pop-it-nums', 'html5', 0, 4, 17, 494, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2601d66f05254503997fbccd03f9ec60/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/pop-it-nums', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Pop all of the correct bubbles in this math fidget bubble game. Practice   \nfinding positive numbers, prime numbers, even numbers and more on each   \nlevel.  A fun way to practice your math vocabulary skills.', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'pop-it-nums.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:55:45', '2022-09-11 22:55:45', NULL),
(2543, 'Valentine Mahjong', 'valentine-mahjong', 'html5', 0, 3, 18, 239, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/96fa5ff13b9a4256843867e56525f572/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/valentine-mahjong', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Wanted 5 Games B.V.', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Valentine Mahjong is a fun and exciting game of Mahjong with extra servings of love! Use your skills, strategy and luck to complete the game! There are some handy features to help you complete the full game.', 'Click on the Mahjong tiles to make connections and clean out the table!', 'valentine-mahjong.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:55:48', '2022-09-11 22:55:48', NULL),
(2544, 'Brain Games', 'brain-games', 'html5', 0, 5, 14, 945, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5c4d61cf406a4a5284b743ab8b99161b/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/brain-games-1', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'trezegames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a 6 in 1 amazing games. Exercise your mind with the genres: Memory, Attention, Math, Logic and Coordination. All games are sequenced, don\'t stop playing!', 'Touch in the screen to play.', 'brain-games.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:55:50', '2022-09-11 22:55:50', NULL),
(2545, 'Petzoong', 'petzoong', 'html5', 0, 4, 14, 443, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/03debbac06d447e79ff1d4ac16783a60/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/petzoong', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'bestphysics', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Petzoong is a fun arcade matching mahjong game. It a simple yet fun game to play featuring cute animals and background animal images. All you have to do is match the mahjong pairs by selecting it. If they are matched it will be removed and you will pass the level once all mahjong pairs are cleared.', 'Petzoong is a casual puzzle game. The little animals of the jungle are coming out, so please match the same animals.', 'petzoong.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:55:53', '2022-09-11 22:55:53', NULL),
(2546, 'Find The Missing Letter', 'find-the-missing-letter', 'html5', 0, 5, 12, 354, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/01825522076b40f091d07ace698440f4/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/find-the-missing-letter', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Pro_Gaming', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You have to choose the missing letter from the alphabet. This is an educational game for the kids. There are 50 Levels to complete. Players can unlock one by one levels. Enjoy!', 'Click on the correct letter on the alphabet on the right side.', 'find-the-missing-letter.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:55:56', '2022-09-11 22:55:56', NULL),
(2547, 'Sudoku Royal', 'sudoku-royal', 'html5', 0, 4, 14, 334, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a96d640dadf44c58a4415ec488926a58/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/sudoku-royal', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Inlogic Software', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Do you think you are a sudoku master? You have 4 difficulties to choose from. Try to pass even the extremely challenging levels. Train your brain with this classic version of sudoku, improve your logic and your memory.\n', 'The common rules of classic sudoku apply. Choose a square and then click on the number you want to fill. Complete the whole 9x9 game board correctly and pass the level. Use pencil mode to take notes or you can also use the hint button.\n', 'sudoku-royal.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:55:59', '2022-09-11 22:55:59', NULL),
(2548, 'Drag and Drop Clothing', 'drag-and-drop-clothing', 'html5', 0, 4, 19, 1035, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1dadf9299ebf4599842d55bca6d7ae19/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/drag-and-drop-clothing', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'nau.kids', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Drag and Drop Clothing\n\nDrag and Drop Clothing is a game developed for children in which they learn the difference between the shapes of objects in a fun way, using their mobile phone, tablet, or computer.\n\nGame developed by:\n\nNau.kids\n', 'Drag each item of clothing to the correct place.', 'drag-and-drop-clothing.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:02', '2022-09-11 22:56:02', NULL),
(2549, 'Elemental Blocks Collapse', 'elemental-blocks-collapse', 'html5', 0, 5, 11, 997, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9079f9bb6aee48a282974c6ec7379f40/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/elemental-blocks-collapse', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Collapse the blocks by tapping groups of horizontally or vertically connected same-color blocks. On each collapse you will obtain a score. The bigger the group you collapse, the higher a score you will get. The status at the bottom will show you the projected score for any selected group.', 'Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.', 'elemental-blocks-collapse.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:05', '2022-09-11 22:56:05', NULL),
(2550, 'Shadow Matching Kids Learning Game', 'shadow-matching-kids-learning-game', 'html5', 0, 5, 13, 204, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9402c5552c95423d81287214001be411/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/shadow-matching-kids-learning-game', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Pro_Gaming', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This game is made for kids to learn and make sharp them minds.\nThere are 50 levels.\nYou and your kids will like this so much.\nKids can play and enjoy this game.\nLearn and Enjoy!', 'Click on left side dot and drag and drop on correct dot on right side to match the shadow.\n\nFor reviewer : this game is not a Christmas game. Game is working fine when I test it. This is shadow matching kids game. Thank you!', 'shadow-matching-kids-learning-game.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:09', '2022-09-11 22:56:09', NULL),
(2551, 'Amazing Jewel', 'amazing-jewel', 'html5', 0, 4, 20, 184, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b8660b2fb0174363ab485763f7fa6aa3/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/amazing-jewel', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Amazing Hedgehog', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You just got the perfect gems and jewels matching game where you match and swap gorgeous jewels to complete the challenging levels. <b>Amazing Jewels Match 3 Game</b> is a brand new high-quality puzzle jewels matching game with the most innovative gameplay.', '✪ Easy to control, easy to play with best graphics\n✪ You just have to match 3 jewels in a row and marge the jewels with your single finger.\n', 'amazing-jewel.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:12', '2022-09-11 22:56:12', NULL),
(2552, 'Football Killer', 'football-killer', 'html5', 0, 3, 10, 92, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6815116ce1e94c1ead20784ed4160c1d/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/football-killer', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Simplicity Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Have you ever dreamed of being a professional footballer?\n\nDo you realize, that in reality it\'s a deadly game?\nThe other footballers, referees, goalkeepers are just there to make you suffer!\nBecause they know about your past. And they are scared.\n\nCool different levels are waiting for you to play – you can show the strength of your shot. But not the referee – he is untouchable… Clever guy…\n\nGraphics and music will take you to the big football stadium!\nTake part in this football adventure now!', 'Click and swipe your mouse to aim, release to shoot!', 'football-killer.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:15', '2022-09-11 22:56:15', NULL),
(2553, 'Math Games', 'math-games', 'html5', 0, 3, 17, 965, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bd829ca7463d48209eb675f0a391c807/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/math-games', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'trezegames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a 8 in 1 amazing math games. Exercise your mind with many math problems involving Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division. All games are sequenced, don\'t stop playing!', 'Touch in the screen to play.', 'math-games.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:17', '2022-09-11 22:56:17', NULL),
(2554, 'Liquid Oranges', 'liquid-oranges', 'html5', 0, 4, 11, 1132, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e5b53b11a0d341b1a26d9870eba633c8/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/liquid-oranges', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Best Kids Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'To make cold juice you need orange. In this game Liquid Oranges you will be preparing it. Squeeze orange slice on the screen by click on the slice with the mouse and hold down the click and try to fill up the empty glass on the bottom of the screen. If you overflow the glass restart the level. Have fun.', 'Use your mouse to play the game or tap on the screen!', 'liquid-oranges.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:20', '2022-09-11 22:56:20', NULL),
(2555, 'Color Circle Puzzle ', 'color-circle-puzzle', 'html5', 0, 4, 20, 407, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9953b51708a347388a9d080ac0f12367/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/color-circle-puzzle', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'kidsgamesplay', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This game is very similar to tic tac toe, but the difference is that at this game you can play with more circles in one field. You can put more circles in one field with different sizes. The goal is to match the circle with the same color. You can match them in horizontal or vertical rows, or diagonal. At the bottom side of the table on the game screen, you will see which circle is coming next to play. So you can do combinations to earn more points. This is an addictive logical game and you can play this game until you have space on the board.', 'Tap on the screen to play this game.', 'color-circle-puzzle.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:23', '2022-09-11 22:56:23', NULL),
(2556, 'Cute Monsters Jigsaw', 'cute-monsters-jigsaw', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 506, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c4f7110173b04de8b835cd541220f5d8/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/cute-monsters-jigsaw', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Best Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Cute Monsters Jigsaw is a free online game in the jigsaw puzzle genre. You have 6 images in three modes to play. Choose one of the modes for the game that you previously choose and start it to play. Drag and drop the pieces to solve the puzzle and create an image. Enjoy, and have fun!', 'Use the mouse to play this game.', 'cute-monsters-jigsaw.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:26', '2022-09-11 22:56:26', NULL),
(2557, 'Craftsman Coloring Pages', 'craftsman-coloring-pages', 'html5', 0, 3, 16, 691, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2567777a198349d5b7f53b892fb85096/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/craftsman-coloring-pages', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'New Kids Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Craftsman Coloring Pages is a free online coloring and kids game, where he exercise her imagination and motor skills while having fun meeting different characters. In this game you will find 18 different pictures which have to be colored. You have 15 different colors to choose. You can also save the colored image. Have fun!', 'Use mouse or touch the screen.', 'craftsman-coloring-pages.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:28', '2022-09-11 22:56:28', NULL),
(2558, 'Time Control', 'time-control', 'html5', 0, 5, 15, 507, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8f4bf80b04f04475abda67a153342087/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/time-control', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'newgamess', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Time Control is a puzzle game where you need to control the red ball. She will move vertically from one point to other. When the ball hits the point you will earn a score. But the squares will rotate around the ball path, so you need to avoid them. For that, you need to control the speed of the ball. Click or tap on the screen to slow the movement of the ball and realize to move normally. Only in that way you can avoid collision with squares. If you hit at the squares the game will be over. So try to do more points as you can and control the ball successfully.', 'Tap on the screen to play this game.', 'time-control.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:31', '2022-09-11 22:56:31', NULL),
(2559, 'Scorpion Solitaire', 'scorpion-solitaire', 'html5', 0, 3, 18, 881, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/befe4aa4ddb74830b515b0a272075ad2/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/scorpion-solitaire-2', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Code This Lab srl', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'If you are a big fan of Klondike and Spider solitaires but you are looking for new variations, you\'ll surely like Scorpion Solitaire. Choose among three different game\'s difficulty: Easy Medium and Hard and complete the solitaire with the least number of moves.', 'Tap cards to move them', 'scorpion-solitaire.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:56:34', '2022-09-11 22:56:34', NULL),
(2607, 'Path Control', 'path-control', 'html5', 0, 3, 13, 79, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/80c6a03fe0f8400ab3dfa9acc78fc940/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/path-control', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'MBG Network', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Aim of the game is to hit the basket with standing ball. By clicking on objects with the mouse you will force them to move left or right and change their location. This way you can make the ball move in the direction you want. When the ball enters the basket, you receive points and proceed to the next level. Have fun.', 'Use your mouse to play the game or tap on the screen!', 'path-control.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:13', '2022-09-11 22:58:13', NULL),
(2608, 'MATH PLASTICINE', 'math-plasticine', 'html5', 0, 4, 11, 639, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/31b2704053ce438185636a93c8256b64/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/math-plasticine', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'nau.kids', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'MATH PLASTICINE\n\nThe MATH PLASTICINE game was developed for children where they will learn quantities, add and subtract in a fun way on their cell phone, tablet or computer.\n\nGame developed by:\n\nnau.kids', 'Click on the correct answer.', 'math-plasticine.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:17', '2022-09-11 22:58:17', NULL),
(2609, 'Atomic Puzzle XMas', 'atomic-puzzle-xmas', 'html5', 0, 5, 12, 555, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/fefcbca28d394a82bd659a237c6640f2/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/atomic-puzzle-xmas', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'IceStone', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Atomic Puzzle in Christmas style now! Clear each level by removing the atoms in the correct order. Can you predict the merging of the molecules so that there’s none left at the end of each level?', 'Use mouse to select combination of atoms.\n1. The colour of the atom you click on does not matter.\n2. Each combination must contain the same coloured atoms.\n3. Only one atom can be left unpaired in each combination.', 'atomic-puzzle-xmas.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:21', '2022-09-11 22:58:21', NULL),
(2610, 'Cats and Dogs Puzzle', 'cats-and-dogs-puzzle', 'html5', 0, 4, 12, 719, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6bfe318f88d3403bb009dce7cfd0f72c/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/cats-and-dogs-puzzle', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'crazyschoolgames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We can say that cats and dogs are the most adorable animals. Combine the pieces and complete the puzzles in this game consisting of photos of cute cats and dogs.', 'LEFT CLICK', 'cats-and-dogs-puzzle.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:24', '2022-09-11 22:58:24', NULL),
(2611, 'Gems Tetriz Match 3', 'gems-tetriz-match-3', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 1016, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/be862067dd6e4d109db2fba9861acac9/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/gems-tetriz-match-3', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Lof Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Use left, right and down keys to move the gems. Use up key to shuffle the gems. Alternatively you can tap or click buttons to do the same. Your target is to fit the blocks to make a linear pattern of gems (horizontally, vertically or diagonally). Achieve target score to complete the level.', 'Left, Right and Down keys or button to move the set of Gems   \nUp key or Rotate button to shuffle the blocks.', 'gems-tetriz-match-3.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:28', '2022-09-11 22:58:28', NULL),
(2612, 'Flat Jumper Game', 'flat-jumper-game', 'html5', 0, 3, 17, 548, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f0f6241541be417f8200ba97a819d421/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/flat-jumper-game', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'kidsgamesplay', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Flat Jumper is a puzzle game where you need to control a jumper ball. The ball will jump over coming platforms. At the bottom of the game will be three balls with different colors. When you touch one of them the color of the jumping ball will change the same as the color of the ball that you touch. The platforms will have the same colors as the balls and the catch is that jumping balls need to match with the platform if they are the same color. So you need to click on balls at the bottom of the game screen to change the jumping ball to get the same color as the platform. Do that and try to pass more platforms as you can.', 'Tap on screen to play this game.', 'flat-jumper-game.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:31', '2022-09-11 22:58:31', NULL),
(2613, 'Three Disks', 'three-disks', 'html5', 0, 4, 17, 789, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/64518707bc174f87b36492f6d4f32ed7/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/three-disks', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'newgamess', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Three disks is a puzzle game where you will control three disks that are going on their orbits. They will move in a circle. From the center of the circles will start to move balls with colors as the colors of the disks. The goal of the game is to catch the ball with a disk that has the same color as the ball. Remember disks can move only in their orbit, so you need to be careful and catch the ball with the right disk. If you catch the ball with the wrong colored disk the game will be over. Tap on the screen to control the disks. They move all in one row so it will be interesting to play.', 'Tap on the screen to play this game.', 'three-disks.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:35', '2022-09-11 22:58:35', NULL),
(2614, 'Mouse', 'mouse', 'html5', 0, 5, 11, 1059, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/eca2c0e4f36c42f7a475d0075995bee0/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/mouse', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Fun Best Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In Mouse game you will also need excellent visual memory, and with it, the mouse is just not doing very well. Help the heroine on every level. It will be located at the bottom of the screen, and in front of it, going up platforms with sharp teeth. There is a passage between them. To be remembered. As soon as you begin to draw a line along which the mouse should move, everything will disappear from the field. You must draw a path from memory and press the Go button. Note that the platforms are still there, they just become invisible in Mouse game.', 'Use mouse or tap on the screen!', 'mouse.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:38', '2022-09-11 22:58:38', NULL),
(2615, 'Wake Up the Box', 'wake-up-the-box', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 276, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/88d7078602364cfd845f7c2796c456c7/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/wake-up-the-box', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', '-', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mr. Box sleeps too much. Wake him up in this physic based puzzle game. Wake Up The Box is a physics-based puzzle game with a lot of fixed and moving parts involved on each level. Use their physics properties to wake the box and see if you can complete all the levels.', 'Instructions in the game.\nSpace – restart level.', 'wake-up-the-box.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:42', '2022-09-11 22:58:42', NULL),
(2616, 'Apple Worm', 'apple-worm', 'html5', 0, 5, 20, 613, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f3bdc4a7675f4dfda0bd1474f7853dab/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/apple-worm', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Gibton', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Apple Worm is an addictive logical puzzle game based on the Snake-like game mechanic (not the traditional snake).\nBend your worm into impossible positions to get to the apple!', 'Get the apple and then escape though the black hole. Use the WASD or Arrow Keys to move. “R” to restart a level.\n\nAlso playable on mobile with built-in joystick.', 'apple-worm.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:45', '2022-09-11 22:58:45', NULL),
(2617, 'Civiballs Origins', 'civiballs-origins', 'html5', 0, 5, 14, 1123, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f10191b27a8543c7a67ad0da51d8f1f0/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/civiballs-origins', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'IP Kovalishin Andrey Nikolaevich', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Choose Greece, Egypt or China and solve the puzzles by cutting the chains. If you get stuck, just try another civilization! Enjoy the classic puzzle with the cut the rope mechanics!', 'mouse/touchscreen', 'civiballs-origins.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:48', '2022-09-11 22:58:48', NULL),
(2618, '2048 X2 Merge Blocks', '2048-x2-merge-blocks', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 747, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/eed4bf8d6226480e987cc2b922d5e1c9/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/2048-x2-merge-blocks', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Inlogic Software', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A combination of the classic game of 2048 and Tetris. The numbers are dropping from above and keep coming. Manage to merge numbers and keep the playing field clean for as long as possible. What is the best merge you can make?\n', 'Tap on the desired columns to drop the falling numbers. Connect identical numbers to merge them into higher numbers. You can also combine more than two numbers for higher multiples.\n', '2048-x2-merge-blocks.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:51', '2022-09-11 22:58:51', NULL),
(2619, 'Apples and Numbers', 'apples-and-numbers', 'html5', 0, 5, 11, 654, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9c58d04d0d944275be0bfe3f037ae60a/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/apples-and-numbers', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'nau.kids', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Apples and Numbers\n\nThe Apples and Numbers game was developed for children where they will learn numerical sequences, quantities and draw numbers in a fun way on their cell phone, tablet or computer.\n\nGame developed by:\n\nNau.kids', 'Number sequences: Drag the correct number into place.\nQuantities: Click on the correct answer.\nDraw numbers: Follow the dots to draw numbers correctly.', 'apples-and-numbers.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:55', '2022-09-11 22:58:55', NULL),
(2620, 'On the edge', 'on-the-edge', 'html5', 0, 4, 17, 823, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a9bb421b494b462a969e546b936040eb/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/on-the-edge', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'BassoGames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'On the Edge is a puzzle game where you have 40 levels to have fun with, with the objective of filling the containers to the limit set.\nJust click until the amount of water needed to fill, you can’t let it overflow or go below the limit. Have fun in these challenges.', 'If you’re using the computer, the mouse does all the action in the game. If you’re on your cell phone, just use the touch.', 'on-the-edge.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:58:59', '2022-09-11 22:58:59', NULL),
(2621, 'Rotating Disks', 'rotating-disks', 'html5', 0, 4, 15, 551, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9f15a4da722b44a7be193cb71e7a81c4/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/rotating-disks', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'newgamess', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Rotating Disks is a puzzle controlled game where the goal of the game is to control two rotating disks. The yellow disks will move both at same time. From the center of the game will coming balls with purple and yellow color. You need to avoid purple balls and to catch yellow balls. Catch more yellow balls as you can during playing this game. If you catch purple ball the game will over. It is not very hard to play but it is interesting and addictive.', 'Tap on screen to rotate disks and to change the direction of move.', 'rotating-disks.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:59:02', '2022-09-11 22:59:02', NULL),
(2622, 'Milk For Cat', 'milk-for-cat', 'html5', 0, 4, 19, 1123, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4fbfd3271b534f289880a198d693273f/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/milk-for-cat', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'MBG Network', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Aim of the game Milk For Cat is to feed various cats with milk. There is a sitting cat and a bag of milk hang on a rope above the cat at a certain height. Milk can swing from side to side like a pendulum. You will have to guess the best moment and cut the rope while the bag of milk is over the cat. If the cat is full, you will receive points for it. Have fun.', 'Use your mouse to play the game or tap on the screen!', 'milk-for-cat.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:59:05', '2022-09-11 22:59:05', NULL),
(2623, 'Color Balls Game', 'color-balls-game', 'html5', 0, 4, 20, 271, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/feffb8b3f3a64e74b732e56993a334d8/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/color-balls-game', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'kidsgamesplay', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Color Balls is a shooter puzzle game. You need to shoot on colored balls that coming from the top of the game screen. There will be different balls in the vertical rolls with different colors. Each ball need to be shoot by bullets with same color as the ball. On the bottom on the screen there is lines with colors as balls. You need to click on the bottom colored lines to shot bullet with color as line. So you can destroy white ball only with white bullet etc. If you shoot with wrong color bullets you will lose lives. You have five lives to play at this game. As you progress in the game the game will be faster and you need to shoot faster. Try this game is it interesting and fun.', 'Tap on screen to play this game.', 'color-balls-game.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:59:09', '2022-09-11 22:59:09', NULL),
(2624, 'Rotating Square', 'rotating-square', 'html5', 0, 5, 15, 444, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b58e522ef70247a2a68be6e66234c719/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/rotating-square', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Fun Best Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Rotating Square is a free online game from genre of puzzle and skill games. This is a game in which you have to control the square and catch the yellow balls.', 'Use mouse on desktop or touch on your mobile device.', 'rotating-square.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:59:12', '2022-09-11 22:59:12', NULL),
(2625, 'The Pyramid Adventure', 'the-pyramid-adventure', 'html5', 0, 4, 15, 726, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/944a538700f141d8bd37d46a91dadc78/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/the-pyramid-adventure', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'RHM Interactive', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Pyramid Adventure game is an adventure that you play in collaboration with 2 Player. Collect diamonds and solve puzzles in historical pyramids. Complete the sculptures in the pyramid and open the locked doors! Use your weapons for the monsters and traps you encounter. To get out of the pyramid, you have to pass a total of 20 levels. Let the adventure begin!\n\n', 'Move: \"W,A,S,D\"\nShot: \"F\"\nJump: \"W\"\nSwitch weapon: \"Q\"\n\nPLAYER 2\nMove: \"ARROW KEYS\"\nGrenade \"L\"\nJump: \"UP ARROW KEY\" \nPick Up Box: \"K\"', 'the-pyramid-adventure.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:59:15', '2022-09-11 22:59:15', NULL),
(2626, 'Cute Kids Trucks Jigsaw', 'cute-kids-trucks-jigsaw', 'html5', 0, 3, 17, 917, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b6804e23c9b2412e93ba1d6d4d2a1b97/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/cute-kids-trucks-jigsaw', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'newgamess', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Cute Kids Trucks is a jigsaw game. At this game you can play with twelve different images with kids cartoon trucks. First select available image and choose in which mode you want to play. You can play at easy mode with 25 pieces, medium with 49 pieces and hard with 100 pieces. If you are beginner at this game choose easy mode and solve the image to go to the next level. Later you can select different mode to play. The game time is unlimited, so you can play as much as you want.', 'Use mouse to drag and drop the pieces into right position.', 'cute-kids-trucks-jigsaw.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 22:59:18', '2022-09-11 22:59:18', NULL),
(2674, 'WordSeeker', 'wordseeker', 'html5', 0, 3, 15, 799, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0d8c781d55134669b2d424e7e427e19a/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/wordseeker', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Take Five', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Train your brain trying to find the correct words in this relaxing vocabulary game. Get your dose of daily brain training with this free puzzle word game. Lovers of classic word games like Scrabble, crosswords or anagrams will love this word hunt and spell vocabulary game. You can share your results with your friends and challenge them to beat you wherever you are!', 'You get 6 tries to guess a 5-letter target word. After each guess, the letters light up in various colors as clues. Green means a letter is correct in this spot; yellow means a letter is elsewhere in the target word; gray means a letter is not in the target word at all.', 'wordseeker.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 23:00:43', '2022-09-11 23:00:43', NULL),
(2675, 'Drawmaster', 'drawmaster', 'html5', 0, 4, 19, 818, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/26a8ee30c6514d58aac378091ddcc526/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/drawmaster', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Zapjee', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Draw master is puzzle game in which you have to draw path for weapon and kill the enemy. Make sure you hit the enemy right. With more than 20+ unique weapons and 30+ different levels can you complete all levels?.The game is fun and the graphics are visually rich. Enrich your idea and creativity and complete the game.', 'Draw path and kill the enemy.', 'drawmaster.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 23:00:46', '2022-09-11 23:00:46', NULL),
