(3427, 'Lipuzz Water Sort Puzzle', 'lipuzz-water-sort-puzzle', 'html5', 0, 4, 17, 622, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e91a77432b204af5aa1383da63f90835/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/lipuzz-water-sort-puzzle', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'UznGames', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You will think a lot and have a lot of fun while playing the Lipuzz game. A great game to exercise memory. The aim of the game is to collect liquids of the same color in a container by transferring the liquids in the containers to each other. The most important rule in the game is that the container you want to pour the liquid into must either be empty or the other container must have the same color liquid. If you can\'t pass the level in the game, you can get another container from the top menu.', 'Touch the screen on mobile devices. Use mouse for computer', 'lipuzz-water-sort-puzzle.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 23:31:09', '2022-09-11 23:31:09', NULL),
(3428, 'Circular Reflection', 'circular-reflection', 'html5', 0, 4, 18, 720, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/034c199f6ff34692989ea50a1ec08fc8/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/circular-reflection', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'newgamess', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Circular Reflection is a game where you need to catch the ball with the shield. You have to be fast and precise to catch the ball. Ball will refuse from shield and will go the other way. Spin around the circle with the shield and do not let the ball go out of the circle. If that happens, the game is over.', 'Tap on the screen to play this game.', 'circular-reflection.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 23:31:12', '2022-09-11 23:31:12', NULL),
(3429, 'Save The Monster', 'save-the-monster', 'html5', 0, 3, 14, 330, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2be57eddbc8949ad9b392e1776b59787/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/save-the-monster', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'kidsgamesplay', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Save The Monster is a kind of puzzle game where you need to move the monster on the board to collect coins and to avoid rockets who want to destroy you.The monster can move from field to field , so you need to find the best way to collect coin. When you collect ten coins the monster will drop the bomb who can destroy some rockets. Play longer as you can, avoid rockets and collect coins.', 'Slide on the screen to play this game.', 'save-the-monster.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 23:31:15', '2022-09-11 23:31:15', NULL),
(3430, '10x10 Gems Deluxe', '10x10-gems-deluxe', 'html5', 0, 5, 14, 318, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2cfc001d7d0b454c8b7e10118879630b/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/10x10-gems-deluxe', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Freak X Apps', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, '10X10 Gems Deluxe is a fun online matching game.\n\nIn this game, you need to make perfect rows and columns of blocks.\n\nPlace the different shapes of blocks strategically under the grid and try to complete rows and columns.\n\nWhen you form a complete row or column, the row or column gets removed from the grid.\n\nBut be careful, while placing the blocks, because the game gets over if there is no space left. So, make a strategy in your mind before placing the blocks.\n\nPlace more and more blocks under the grid to make a high score.\n\nSo, what are you waiting for? Play 10x10 Gems Deluxe and take your tetris skills to the next level.', 'Drag and drop blocks', '10x10-gems-deluxe.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 23:31:19', '2022-09-11 23:31:19', NULL),
(3478, 'Cubic Wall', 'cubic-wall', 'html5', 0, 3, 17, 633, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2870a864bb444298a5a7d7f83a0c31ef/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/cubic-wall', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'newgamess', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Cubic Wall is a game where you need to control the wall who is with bricks with different colors. From the top of the game will fall balls with colors as the bricks. The goal of the game is to catch the ball with brick that have same color. It is not easy but when you start to play you can estimate the speed of movement of the ball and the wall and when they can match.', 'Tap on the screen to move the wall.', 'cubic-wall.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 23:33:12', '2022-09-11 23:33:12', NULL),
(3479, 'Rope Bawling', 'rope-bawling', 'html5', 0, 5, 18, 773, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/149bb25895684e05badcc07c3c3dfc06/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/rope-bawling', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Fun Best Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Rope Bawling – This is a game in which you need to cut the rope to help the bowling balls destroy the skittles, on your way there will be boxes on the laces and a variety of moving platforms.', 'Use mouse or touch the screen!', 'rope-bawling.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-11 23:33:15', '2022-09-11 23:33:15', NULL),
