(4345, 'fill one line puzzle game', 'fill-one-line-puzzle-game', 'html5', 0, 4, 16, 82, '1', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4587342b79004a12812adc1da2796f84/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/fill-one-line-puzzle-game', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'ZKgame', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Sharpen your mind with a connect-the-block-style one-line brain training puzzle game.\nA simple but addictive one-line puzzle game that’s completely free to play.\n\nYour brain becomes more active the more you play.\nDuring your commute, before you sleep… enjoy downtime with brain training.\n\nThe rules are extremely simple.\nJust fill in all of the blocks using only one line.\n\nUse hints for puzzles that are too hard to solve.\nHints are also free, of course.\n\n4 levels of difficulty.\nA whopping 2,000 puzzles.\nDon’t get too cozy—the puzzles get harder as you go along.\n\nOne-line puzzles are mathematical problems with origins in the early 18th century. First posed in Königsberg, the original puzzle revolved around the town’s Pregel River.\nMathematical thinking is said to increase work efficiency and prevent aging.\nWhether math is your bane or your forte, be sure to give this game a try.\nYou’re sure to get hooked on these puzzles!', 'Sharpen your mind with a connect-the-block-style one-line brain training puzzle game.\nA simple but addictive one-line puzzle game that’s completely free to play.\n\nYour brain becomes more active the more you play.\nDuring your commute, before you sleep… enjoy downtime with brain training.\n\nThe rules are extremely simple.\nJust fill in all of the blocks using only one line.', 'fill-one-line-puzzle-game.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-12 00:07:33', '2022-09-12 00:07:33', NULL),
(4346, 'Philatelic Escape Fauna Album', 'philatelic-escape-fauna-album', 'html5', 0, 5, 18, 123, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/494b16eddab040469d5296df1a074d06/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/philatelic-escape-fauna-album', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Age Simple Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We present you the game Philatelic Escape - Fauna Album. This interesting game is made in the style of Escape room. Your objective is to find ten hidden postage stamps and the stamp album. There are many puzzles waiting for you here. Solve puzzles by clicking at the items around, open locked doors  and find stamps. Be careful, do not miss any detail. Use logical thinking, creativity and your brains to crack different passwords. But first, you need to get inside the apartment. Good luck!', 'Use mouse, click on things around.', 'philatelic-escape-fauna-album.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-12 00:07:36', '2022-09-12 00:07:36', NULL),
(4347, 'Fishing and Lines', 'fishing-and-lines', 'html5', 0, 5, 15, 549, '0', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bd308e73b0ae457ba8f21504c37e1385/?gd_sdk_referrer_url=https://gamedistribution.com/games/fishing-and-lines', 'https://gamedistribution.com', 'en', 'Age Simple Games', 28, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Meet the exciting game Fishing and Lines. We decided to combine balls, lines and fishing in one game. And here’s what we got. You are playing balls and enjoying fishing. A puzzle logical game allows you to learn about wide variety of river and sea fish species.\nYou can catch 140 species of different fish depending on the color combinations of the balls, the length of the line and the number of lines. Depending on the type of the fish, you can earn different amount of points (coins). You can see your catch in the fish cage. If you made a move and the line did not form, three new colored balls will appear on the field. You can see which balls will appear near or on the field. The game continues until the field is completely filled with balls or the goal of the level is reached.\n     Amateur fishing for beginners or players who prefer an easy playing. The objective of this mode is to score as many points as possible and catch as many fish as possible.\n     Fishing Levels is a game mode with 150 levels and different tasks. The goal of this mode is to complete all tasks and get the maximum number of stars. \n     Fishing Pro is an interesting variation of the classic version of Color Lines. The minimum length of the lines is 5 balls of the same color.\n     Tournaments is game mode where you can take part in 5 tournaments and win bronze, silver or gold cups.', 'The goal of the game is to catch as many fish as possible by moving the balls from one cell to another and creating lines of three or more identical balls horizontally, vertically or diagonally.', 'fishing-and-lines.jpeg', 1, 1, '2022-09-12 00:07:39', '2022-09-12 00:07:39', NULL),
